<div id="banner">
	<h1>802.11b Theremin (two geeky pursuits that geek well together)</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Seth Schoen has built <a href="http://vitanuova.loyalty.org/2003-01-16.html">an theremin in shell using an 802.11b card as a sensor</a>. <em>How cool!</em></p>

<p>In other news, the <a href="http://spamconference.org/">spam conference</a> is today and <a href="http://www.internationalanswer.org/campaigns/j18/j18endorse.html">the DC/SF march against war</a> is tomorrow. (Sadly, I won&#8217;t make any of them, but at least the spam conference is being webcasted.</p>

